<div class="content" id="middle">
  <h1>Joining Shadowclan</h1>
  <p><a href="joining.html">Why join</a> | <a href="expectations.html">Expectations
    of Members</a> | <a href="procedure.html">Joining
    procedure</a> </p>

  <h3>Why Join?</h3>
  <p>Shadowclan is an open-membership guild dedicated to roleplaying a misunderstood, perhaps 'evil' race. 
	We started in Ultima Online as a guild of player-character Orcs;
    since then we have opened branches in numerous other games, always dedicated
    to playing a limited selection of 'evil' (or, rather, 'misunderstood') races,
    providing enjoyable enemies for the mainstream player to oppose. In Lineage II,
    we are Orcs and certain Dark elf classes, races who allied to fight the infestation of humans and elves. </p>
  <p>As a guild, we are dedicated both to high-quality roleplaying, and to highly
    effective PVP. We roleplay our character fully and at all times. We do not talk smack with our enemies; our
    goal is to create a vibrant, immersive, lore-compliant, and deadly nation. 
	Note that we do not automatically kill all the 'pinkis' on sight; we
    will collect tribute when convenient, and may occasionally even coordinate
    military actions with non-Shadowclan guilds against a common foe.</p>
  <h2>&nbsp;</h2>
