<div class="content" id="right">
  <h2>Dark Elves</h2>
  <p> Evil and aloof. Dark elves have been betrayed by humans and elves, 
  and thus hate them even more than the orcs do. 
  Dark elves have grown to distrust even dark elves in other clans. 
  They see orcs as primitive, and the dark elves allied with the 
  Shadowclan orcs do so to further their own ends. The alliance is 
  strong though, and though the two races taunt each other, there is 
  an underlying respect between the two races for each others strengths 
  and their willingness to work together. </p>
